{"tid":158990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嫌警口臭用手撥變襲警    城巴女司機上訴得直","createTime":"2017-03-16T16:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T01:09:31.000Z","uid":48093,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed115fa206b53bc948a7e5f97f415b97188f04a9","tid":158990,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170317/large/1489680051_a04d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170317%2Flarge%2F1489680051_a04d.jpg&h=7edcb11a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名女城巴司機因涉欠交罰款而被通緝，遭警長要求帶返警署調查後，被指突然發難襲擊警長的肩和手臂。女司機受審時辯稱是警長趨前向她吹了一口氣，因警長口氣難聞，她才舉高手一撥以保護自己。女司機早前被裁定襲警罪成，她向高等法院提上訴，法官昨指閉路電視未能拍到襲擊一刻，並指警長將頭伸前的行為不恰當，而警方兩名證人的證供不脗合，故裁定女司機上訴得直。<br />\n<br />\n案發時涉案現場發生交通意外，警長到場後，發現城巴女司機、即上訴人邵玉英為通緝人士，故表示要帶她返警署，他指跟着遭邵襲擊，左前臂留下4條傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n暫委法官彭中屏昨在判詞指，閉路電視只拍到警長案發時狀似頗為激動，突然踏前一步，將頭伸前衝向邵的臉，邵隨即舉高右手快速掃了一下；警長即時制服邵，但見不到警長所指邵用左手拳打他的手臂和心口，或嘗試咬他的手臂。彭官指警長突將頭伸前接近邵的臉，行為看來不恰當，可以令人受驚甚至構成襲擊。警長曾上庭作供，卻不能解釋為何他要將頭伸前。<br />\n<br />\n彭官續指，醫生報告沒支持警長受傷的證據，反而有支持邵受傷的內容，而警長與另一警員就案發經過的口供都不脗合，案中存在疑點。<br />\n上訴時沒律師代表的邵稱，因警長向她吹了一口氣，她才舉高手保護自己，沒有打到警長；她續稱警長的表情顯示他不停罵她，行為挑釁而且濫權。彭官認為警長突然將頭伸向邵的臉，令邵作出保護反應並非不合常理，故裁定她上訴得直，推翻裁判法院的定罪，及擱置兩周的刑期。"},{"pid":"b4374fd3d91046e13001ee7cccfdea1768c1e92c","tid":158990,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6f025fb01b8df89cc5d86f32783a902af3f746","tid":158990,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"口臭影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf9acaf5cb429a77ca89aa23d339d23de7f2c7a","tid":158990,"uid":63350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"又有醜聞，我信條警犬向人噴氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10248770fdf4783b9db37f712bf0a26f1524a9ff","tid":158990,"uid":47986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"bb38e66a06977bf8661f6a097a6501e2f13d2272","tid":158990,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2c23d6f0b5eecd34a2e2b0ddba967cdb0da16a","tid":158990,"uid":8514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾梗係有臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f033fe950b1c1e2e6976b8f6f0dcb43451bc338a","tid":158990,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61d16015447c74a4e6436690a1bfab5804d73e89","tid":158990,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"生化襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fc0defd11cf0ce4557a2db17c8365bcde1d3c8","tid":158990,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19128e17a2b85de921b371aed55783c539c9d119","tid":158990,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:29:42.000Z","msg":"突個龜頭埋嚟"},{"pid":"32d51f1fecf771d938d3f4892c378165b4f24019","tid":158990,"uid":40607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:30:14.000Z","msg":"屌？，<br />\n口臭就唔好哄咁埋la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0637b36714d461485b251e0f8e38bf9e19ac5f3e","tid":158990,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:33:08.000Z","m